    "Another way is to apply clustering algorithms, e.g., K-Means or DBSCAN, on doc-topic distributions (Zhao et al 2021b).",
    "The clustering performance can be measured by Purity and Normalized Mutual Information (NMI, Manning et al 2008).",
    "Finally, researchers visualize topic models for evaluation.",
    "The typical visualization method is to show the top words of topics and doc-topic distributions, such as using pyLDAvis foot_3 (Sievert and Shirley 2014) or word cloud.",
